attributes.title: A waste of my time✨🧚🏽
attributes.review: I dont recommend this app to anyone. I downloaded it and I had to wait 69 days for it to me be installed in my phone. When I opened the app my phone went black and overheated. Because of this app I now get text messages and phone calls from scammers. All this app does is breach ur information and make it easier for telemarketers to contact u. It also drained my battery to 5% even though the app was only open for 2 minutes. I really don’t want anyone to go through what I went through to even get the app open so I think Apple should just take it down because this app is messing up our phones and the software isn’t good either. So I wish I could just give zero stars but I guess one star is the closest. I usually get good service here under the sea but this app really messed up my phone and it’s hard to get phones fixed down here in the ocean. So to all my sea creatures out there and all my humans up there don’t do it. This messes up ur phone so bad it makes dropping ur phone in water look good. Me waiting for what felt like a decade for the app to download even with the good service I had down here in the sea: 👁👄👁. 🧚‍♂️💫Zero out of ten, wouldn’t recommend💖✨
